{"Id":489,"LanguageCodes":["zh","zho"],"Name":"zho-muhammadmakin","Author":"Muhammad Makin","Language":"Chinese(simplified)","Description":"Chinese(simplified)","Direction":"ltr","Source":"https://quranenc.com/check/chinese_makin/v1.0.0-csv.1 , https://quranenc.com/en/browse/chinese_makin , https://quranenc.com ,","Translations":[{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":77,"Text":"这确是宝贵的《古兰经》，"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":78,"Text":"记录在珍藏的经本中，"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":79,"Text":"只有纯洁者才得抚摸那经本。"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":80,"Text":"《古兰经》是从全世界的主降示的。"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":81,"Text":"难道你们藐视这训辞，"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":82,"Text":"而以否认代替感谢吗？"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":83,"Text":"（你们）怎么不在灵魂到将死者的咽喉的时候"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":84,"Text":"那时候，你们大家看着他，"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":85,"Text":"我比你们更临近他，但你们不晓得，"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":86,"Text":"如果你们不是受报应的，"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":87,"Text":"你们怎不使灵魂复返于本位呢？如果你们是说实话的。"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":88,"Text":"如果他是被眷顾的，"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":89,"Text":"那么，他将享受舒适、给养与恩泽的乐园；"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":90,"Text":"如果他是幸福者，"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":91,"Text":"那么，一般幸福的人将对他说：祝你平安！"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":92,"Text":"如果他是迷误的、否认复活者，"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":93,"Text":"那么，他将享受沸水的款待，"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":94,"Text":"和烈火的烧灼。"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":95,"Text":"这确是无可置疑的真理。"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":96,"Text":"故你应当颂扬你的主的大名。"},{"SurahNumber":57,"VerseNumber":1,"Text":"天地万物，都赞颂安拉超绝万物，他确是万能的，确是至睿的。"},{"SurahNumber":57,"VerseNumber":2,"Text":"天地的国权，归他所有；他能使人生，能使人死；他对于万事，是全能的。"},{"SurahNumber":57,"VerseNumber":3,"Text":"他是前无始后无终的，是极显著极隐微的，他是全知万物的。"}]}